OL,3,CLiverpool falls silent to mark 35
OL,4,Cyears since Hillsborough disaster
OL,6,FLiverpool fell silent 35 years on from
OL,7,Fthe .
OL,9,F97 men, women and children died in the
OL,10,Ftragedy at the FA Cup semi-final
OL,11,Fbetween Liverpool and Nottingham
OL,12,FForest on 15 April 1989.
OL,14,FAt 3.06pm ` the time the match was
OL,15,Fstopped ` a minute's silence was
OL,16,Fobserved in Exchange Flags, behind
OL,17,FLiverpool Town Hall, and by players
OL,18,Fand staff at the football club.
