OL,4,Cyears since Hillsborough disaster
OL,6,FWriting on X, previously known as
OL,7,FTwitter, he said: "Today on the 35th
OL,8,Fanniversary of Hillsborough, I'll be
OL,9,Fthinking about those lost, their
OL,10,Ffamilies, and their enduring courage
OL,11,Fand determination to pursue justice.
OL,13,F"Making the Hillsborough Law a reality
OL,14,Fwould be a priority of my Labour
OL,15,Fgovernment."JA specially designed
OL,16,Fbench to recognise survivors of the
OL,17,Fdisaster was unveiled at Anfield on
OL,18,FFriday, 12 April.
