OL,6,FInquests into the deaths, held after
OL,7,Fthe original verdicts were quashed
OL,8,Ffollowing the Hillsborough Independent
OL,9,FPanel report, concluded in 2016 and
OL,10,Ffound the victims were and errors by
OL,11,Fthe police and ambulance service
OL,12,Fcaused or contributed to the deaths.
OL,14,FThe match commander on the day, David
OL,15,FDuckenfield, was charged with gross
OL,16,Fnegligence manslaughter in 2017, but
OL,17,Fwas cleared in 2019 at a retrial held
OL,18,Fafter the jury in his first trial was
OL,19,Funable to reach a verdict.
